in Linux kernel forward slashes / instead of backwards slashed for the files path
adb devices
adb shell   -> only 1 device
adb -s emular-5554 shell  -> for more than 1 device
su    -> grant root access
ls -l       -> show the folders
cd data/data/com.vcmanea.a11_tasktimer_app/databases -> reach the app folder
sqlite3 TaskTimer.db    -> open the database
.schema -> show the tables after is just sql
adb shell setprop log.tag.SQLiteQueryBuilder DEBUG          ->      DEBUG LOG WITH THE SqLiteQuierbyBuilder class -> activate the LOGS







